            "title": "沃爾核材超購逾568倍   1 手中籤率0.33%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">沃爾核材(09981）香港公開發售部分超額認購約568.58倍，最終發售價每股H股20.09元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"沃爾核材官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/002130-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"沃爾核材官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/002130-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">沃爾核材官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">認購一手200股中籤率0.33%，認購7萬股即350手方穩獲1手。輝立暗盤收報21元，比定價升4.5%，一手帳面賺182元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">沃爾核材為熱縮材料及通信電纜製造商，瓴集團旗下HHLR、Jump Trading、惠州惠聯、深圳新世界、霧凇、SCV Alpha、Yield Royal及易亞投資管理等16名基石投資者合共認購4823.18萬股，佔發售總數34.45%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659606-%e6%b2%83%e7%88%be%e6%a0%b8%e6%9d%90%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc%e9%80%be568%e5%80%8d-1-%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%870-33",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/002130-Web3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 09:15:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "永利澳門上季經調整後物業EBITDAR按年跌7.45%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">永利澳門 (01128)控股股東Wynn Resorts Limited公布，澳門業務上季經調整後的物業EBITDAR為2.7億美元，按年跌7.45%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：永利澳門官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_01288-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：永利澳門官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_01288-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：永利澳門官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2025全年計，經調整後的物業EBITDAR為10.85億美元，跌7.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其中，永利皇宮上季經營收益近6億美元，按年升5.9%，經調整後的物業EBITDAR為1.6億美元，跌11.4%。全年計經營收益23.1億美元，升4%，經調整後的物業EBITDAR跌6.9%至6.8億美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">永利澳門上季經營收益3.7億美元，升2.1%，經調整後的物業EBITDAR為近1.1億美元，跌0.7%，全年計經營收益14.1億美元，跌3.7%，經調整後的物業EBITDAR跌9%，至4億美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659599-%e6%b0%b8%e5%88%a9%e6%be%b3%e9%96%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e5%be%8c%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%adebitdar%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c7-45",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_01288-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 09:02:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期挫344點   ADR低水277點   重磅股弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期跌344點或1.28%，報26653。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_09888-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_09888-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指上日收市低水277點或1.03%，報26754點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">百度(09888) ADR折合港元計收報135.21元，較香港收市價低3.5% ;阿里巴巴(09988) ADR折合港元計收報155.1元，較香港收市價低2.2% ; 騰訊(00700) ADR折合港元計收報526.63元，較香港收市價低1.7%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報135.69元，較香港收市價低2.7% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣82.41元，較香港收市價低水1.7% ; 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣412.32元，較香港收市價低0.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659589-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%ab344%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4277%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e8%82%a1%e5%bc%b1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 08:57:17",
